fields.description:
*+Objective+*
 * Improve related ad relevancy to user so we can improve engagement with Related Ad for further lead generation.
 * Expose more attributes on related ad to improve CTR

*+BE Implementation+*
 # Location: within the same L3 location
 # Price: 10% deviation; exclude contact me option
 # Type: same type; Desarollo and Venta are treated as the same type.
 # # of bedroom: same #
 # # of bathroom: same #
 # Exclude listing from the same seller
 # If step 1 to 6 can't provide sufficient listing, we fall back price at 5%.
 # If step 6 still can't provide sufficient listing, we fall back # of bedroom and # of bath room, +1 for both attributes.
 # According to the result, BEp provide new data points to support additional FE design - # of bedroom, # of bathroom, # of garage

*+FE Implementation+*
 * Add in # of bedroom, # of bathroom, # of garage info

*+Mock-up+*
 * Desktop - [https://zpl.io/a3vyr3x|https://zpl.io/brrLpJ7]
 * Mobile - [https://zpl.io/2pdWr8N|https://zpl.io/V0EAkDw]

*+AB testing set-up+*
 * Control - current related ad
 * Testing - new algorithm and display
 * Main metrics - session with click on related ad/ all session; RE VIP improves 58% of this metric and it's now 14%+.

items.toString:
*+Objective+*
 * To improve the engagement with Landing Page, we want to make sure there is a path for user to come back to Landing Page from unit VIP.

*+Implementation+*
 * Below description section, we will show Project this unit belongs to so user can click through to ND Landing Page
 * Image - first image of the Project (ND Landing Page)
 * # of unit means # of unit on ND Landing Page unit list
 * Desde $xxxx means the lowest price of the unit on ND Landing Page unit list
 * Description - content comes from ND Landing Page description and we truncated to 3 rows only
 * Amenities - only show the top 6 items
 * When user clicks image, ver detalles button on the image, truncated dots, ver detalles button at the bottom, we will redirect user to ND Landing Page.

*+Mock-up+*
 * Journey - [https://zpl.io/anmzQBA]
 * Desktop - [https://zpl.io/aBE3mr0]
 * Mobile - [https://zpl.io/aBE3mr0]
This issue is cloned by ULIVZ-38282
